:\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"ItemList\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/lodi-ca#itemlist\",\"name\":\"Indoor Dog Park In Lodi\",\"description\":\"Top-rated dog parks and facilities in Lodi, CA\",\"numberOfItems\":5,\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dream-big-training-center\",\"name\":\"Dream Big Training Center\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dream-big-training-center\",\"description\":\"Dream Big Training Center is the beating heart of Lodi's canine community, offering a dog park experience tailored to social, curious pups. Located in Lodi, CA, the park is tucked near 19681 Brandt...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Lodi\",\"addressRegion\":\"CA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sunset-kennels\",\"name\":\"Sunset Kennels\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sunset-kennels\",\"description\":\"Sunset Kennels is the beating heart of Lodi's canine community, offering a dog park experience tailored to social, curious pups. Located in Lodi, CA, the park is tucked near 19705 N Ray Rd, Lodi, CA...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Lodi\",\"addressRegion\":\"CA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sycamore-lane-kennels\",\"name\":\"Sycamore Lane Kennels\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sycamore-lane-kennels\",\"description\":\"Sycamore Lane Kennels anchors Lodi's dog-loving rhythm as a dog park that marries expansive play yards with concierge-level care. Located in Lodi, CA, the park is tucked near 5111 W Sargent Rd, Lodi,...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Lodi\",\"addressRegion\":\"CA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/all-dogs-sports-park-llc\",\"name\":\"All Dogs Sports Park, LLC\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/all-dogs-sports-park-llc\",\"description\":\"Perched in Lodi, All Dogs Sports Park, LLC delivers a dog park experience where energetic romps and mindful training feel perfectly balanced. Located in Lodi, CA, the park is tucked near 5111 W...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Lodi\",\"addressRegion\":\"CA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":5,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/vinewood-park\",\"name\":\"Vinewood Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/vinewood-park\",\"description\":\"Vinewood Park anchors Lodi's dog-loving rhythm as a dog park that marries expansive play yards with concierge-level care. Located in Lodi, CA, the park is tucked near 931 Virginia Ave, Lodi, CA 95242...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Lodi\",\"addressRegion\":\"CA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}25:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2d\"}}]\n2e:T50c,{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I take my dog in Lodi, CA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Lodi offers excellent off-leash play at Vinewood Dog Park and Beckman Dog Park (the city's largest). Lodi Lake Park also features a dedicated off-leash area near the Mokelumne River on its southeast side.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are Lodi wineries dog-friendly?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, Lodi is famous for its dog-friendly vineyards. Oak Farm Vineyards, Intercoastal Vineyards, m2 Wines, and Harney Lane all welcome leashed pups on their beautiful patios and grounds.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I walk my dog at Lodi Lake?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Absolutely. While dogs must be on a leash in most areas and are restricted from the nature area, they can enjoy the dedicated off-leash zone near Turner Road and leashed walks along the Mokelumne River.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Which restaurants in Lodi have dog-friendly patios?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Many downtown spots welcome pups, including Lodi Beer Co., West Oak Nosh, and Pietros Trattoria. The Dancing Fox and Five Window Beer Co. also offer pet-friendly outdoor seating.\"}}]}26:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2e\"}}]\n27:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"California Dog Parks\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Lodi\\\"}]}\"}}]\n28:[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n29:[\"$\",\"$L2f\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"California Dog Parks\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Lodi\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Indoor Dog Park In Lodi\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-chip-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Verified parks\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"5\"}],\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Wine region\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"Dog-friendly\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Discover Lodi's wine country charm with river-adjacent trails and premium dog training facilities.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Lodi, California, famously immortalized in song and celebrated as a world-class wine region, offers a surprisingly robust landscape for dog families. Situated in the fertile San Joaquin Valley, the city is defined by its deep agricultural roots and a community that treats its four-legged residents as integral members. While Lodi is renowned for its old-vine Zinfandels, its pet infrastructure is anchored by expansive off-leash zones and river-adjacent trails. The local dog culture is social and active, with residents often mixing morning play sessions with weekend excursions to pet-friendly tasting rooms. The \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.lodi.gov\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"City of Lodi\"}],null,\" maintains several key facilities, ensuring that whether you are a local handler or a visitor exploring the Central Valley, you have access to clean, safe, and engaging environments for your pup to thrive.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Off-leash activity is centered at Beckman Dog Park, the city’s largest facility, which features dedicated sections for different size breeds and plenty of room for high-energy sprints. For a more scenic experience, Lodi Lake Park offers a designated off-leash area near the Mokelumne River, allowing dogs to enjoy the cool breezes coming off the water. Beyond the parks, Lodi’s world-famous wineries like Oak Farm Vineyards and Intercoastal Vineyards provide stunning, dog-friendly patios where pets are welcomed with open arms. After a day of exploration, local favorites like Lodi Beer Co. offer pup-friendly outdoor dining, making the city a complete destination for pet-centric living. From the shaded runs of Vinewood Dog Park to the sunset views at a vineyard, Lodi seamlessly blends agricultural charm with premium pet-friendly amenities.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],\"$L31\"]}],\"$L32\"]}],\"$L33\"]}]}],\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\",\"$L3e\",\"$L3f\"]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"IndoorDogPark\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"children\":\"About us\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/partners\",\"children\":\"Partners\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"Discover\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"chil