e Mokelumne River corridor offer scenic, temperature-regulated paths perfect for morning exercise.\"}],\"topAmenities\":[],\"insightIntro\":\"Lodi blends agricultural charm with premium pet amenities. From world-class wineries to shaded river runs, it’s a premier destination for active dog families.\"}]}]}]\n36:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"className\":\"city-comparison-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L4b\",null,{\"parks\":\"$35:props:children:props:children:props:parks\",\"cityName\":\"Lodi\"}]}]}]\n37:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"className\":\"park-collections-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"section-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Curated collections\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Choose the vibe that fits your next outing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Segmented park groupings built from live data so you can jump straight to the experiences that matter most.\"}]]}],false,[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"park-type-guide-wrapper\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L4c\",null,{\"parksByType\":{\"Dog Park\":[\"$35:props:children:props:children:props:parks:0\",\"$35:props:children:props:children:props:parks:1\",\"$35:props:children:props:children:props:parks:2\",\"$35:props:children:props:children:props:parks:3\",\"$35:props:children:props:children:props:parks:4\"]}}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"style\":{\"marginTop\":80,\"paddingTop\":80,\"borderTop\":\"1px solid #f1f5f9\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"section-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Local Districts\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":[\"Where to play in \",\"Lodi\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Semantic cluste