.813163+00:00\"}],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJc2KUMW-gmoARSiGH_0I-7XE\",\"name\":\"Vinewood Park\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$2f\",\"slug\":\"vinewood-park\",\"address\":\"931 Virginia Ave\",\"street\":\"931 Virginia Ave\",\"city\":\"Lodi\",\"state\":\"CA\",\"zipCode\":\"95242\",\"full_address\":\"931 Virginia Ave, Lodi, CA 95242\",\"latitude\":38.1236348,\"longitude\":-121.2954646,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJc2KUMW-gmoARSiGH_0I-7XE\",\"phone\":\"(209) 333-6742\",\"website\":\"https://www.lodi.gov/Facilities/Facility/Details/Vinewood-Park-3\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.5,\"reviewCount\":230,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"dog_park\",\"park\",\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[{\"question\":\"What should I bring for check-in at Vinewood Park?\",\"answer\":\"Bring proof of current rabies and core vaccinations, a leash for entry and exit, and an ID tag with up-to-date contact info to breeze through check-in at Vinewood Park. Download the waiver from https://www.lodi.gov/Facilities/Facility/Details/Vinewood-Park-3 and submit your dog profile before your visit.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"How does pricing work at Vinewood Park?\",\"answer\":\"Vinewood Park offers flexible memberships and punch cards so you can tailor visits to your routine. Contact the desk for the latest promotions or multi-dog discounts.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"Which amenities does Vinewood Park offer?\",\"answer\":\"The team rotates toys, agility props, and splash features weekly so repeat visits to Vinewood Park never feel stale. Expect shaded seating, rinse stations, and staff roaming the yards to keep playgroups safe.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"When is Vinewood Park open and where do I park?\",\"answer\":\"Hours rotate with weather and staffing, so call ahead to confirm current play blocks. Street and shared-lot parking is available nearby; arrive a few minutes early to grab a spot. Use posted signage around Lodi to navigate any temporary closures.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"How do I contact the team at Vinewood Park?\",\"answer\":\"For reservations, temperament assessments, or party rentals, call (209) 333-6742, and visit https://www.lodi.gov/Facilities/Facility/Details/Vinewood-Park-3. The concierge team at Vinewood Park typically replies within one business day.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"}],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"}],\"cityName\":\"Lodi\",\"insightCards\":[{\"tag\":\"Park Space\",\"title\":\"Expansive Off-Leash Zones\",\"copy\":\"Beckman and Vinewood parks provide massive, fully-fenced areas where dogs can sprint and socialize safely under mature valley oaks.\",\"accent\":true},{\"tag\":\"Wine Country\",\"title\":\"Pup-Friendly Vintners\",\"copy\":\"Lodi’s famous wineries like Oak Farm and Intercoastal welcome leashed companions on their stunning, expansive patios.\"},{\"tag\":\"Nature Trails\",\"title\":\"River-Adjacent Walks\",\"copy\":\"Lodi Lake and the Mokelumne River corridor offer scenic, temperature-regulated paths perfect for morning exercise.\"}],\"topAmenities\":[],\"insightIntro\":\"Lodi blends agricultural charm with premium pet amenities. From world-class wineries to shaded river runs, it’s a premier destination for active dog families.\"}]}]}]\n17:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"className\":\"city-comparison-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"parks\":\"$16:props:children:props:children:props:parks\",\"cityName\":\"Lodi\"}]}]}]\n18:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"className\":\"park-collections-section\",\"children\"